</Breadcrumb>

<h2>Welcome to Blazor Components</h2>
<p>Blazor Components is a open source library.</p>

<section>
    <h3>Breadcrumb Component</h3>
    <p>
        <Breadcrumb>
            <BreadcrumbItem Uri="#">Home</BreadcrumbItem>
